title: George Younce with Ernie Haase & Signature Sound CD
description:
For more than 50 years, Cathedrals co-founder George Younce's bass voice was adored by millions of fans. Backed by Ernie Haase and Signature Sound, these remastered tracks of George's most requested songs bring the popular performer to life again. Includes "Suppertime," "I Know Who Holds Tomorrow," "Beyond the Sunset," "There's Room at the Cross for You," and much more.

	
1. Love Was In The Room
2. At The Cross	
3. Beyond The Sunset
4. I Know Who Holds Tomorrow
5. Room At The Cross
6. Suppertime
7. You Will Get Your Reward Someday
8. The Journey's End
9. Sometimes This Is Heaven To Me
10. Silent Night
